# I'm Jesse Talavera-Greenberg.

I love building things in native code (C, C++, Rust) that bring people joy.
Usually that involves something related to games,
but I can also whip up a good CLI tool or web app
that'll make your day easier.

I'm also known to write good documentation
that distills complex topics into practical advice.
